      <!-- Lead paragraph -->
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Ten-letter words in Scrabble are rare gems. You need 3 tiles already on the board positioned perfectly alongside your 7 rack tiles. When it works, you earn the bingo bonus plus a word that stretches across premium squares like nothing else. Here's everything you need to know about these elite plays.</p>

