        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏷️ TERRORIZED — 20pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Common rack tiles + Z, easy to visualize from TERRORIZE + D</p></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Related Articles -->
      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
